article.description: Tommy Rutherford tied his career high with 20 points on 9-of-10 shooting as UC Irvine easily beat Louisiana-Lafayette 92-67 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Rutherford carries UC Irvine past Louisiana-Lafayette 92-67
article.linkText: Rutherford carries UC Irvine past Louisiana-Lafayette 92-67
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- Tommy Rutherford tied his career high with 20 points on 9-of-10 shooting as UC Irvine easily beat Louisiana-Lafayette 92-67 on Tuesday. Collin Welp had 15 points for UC Irvine (4-4). Eyassu Worku added 13 points, and John Edgar Jr. had 12 points, nine rebounds and five assists. Rutherford scored 10 points in the first half as UCI led 40-33. P.J. Hardy had 18 points for the Ragin' Cajuns (4-3). Kobe Julien added 13 points and eight rebounds, and Trajan Wesley had 11 points and six assists.
